      <section class="instructions general">
        <h1 class="header">Brick-Match</h1>
        <h2 class="header">What's This</h2>
        <p class="general">This is a Lego themed matching game that will
          introduce you to some common lego pieces. Your score will be tracked
          and displayed on the right. For further instructions you may read the
          "How to Play" section</p>
        <h2 class="header">How to Play</h2>
        <p class="general">Match pairs of Lego-themed cards to win points. Click
          on a card to reveal it, then try to find its match. The game ends when
          all pairs are matched.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="main">
